### 3.5
### Read
GET http://localhost:8080/products/

### Create

POST http://localhost:8080/products/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 5,
    "name": "Arbuz",
    "price": 15.0
}

### Update

PUT http://localhost:8080/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Pomarancza",
    "price": 3.5
}

### Delete

DELETE http://localhost:8080/products/3


### 4.0
### Kategorie

GET http://localhost:8080/categories

### Dodaj kategorie

