Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3,
  "name": "Pieczywo"
}

### Aktualizuj kategorie

PUT http://localhost:8080/categories/3

{
  "id": 3,
  "name": "Nabial"
}


### Usun kategorie
DELETE http://localhost:8080/categories/3

